---
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
  <title>Weekly Menu | A Jammin Life</title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Josefin+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet"
  />
</head>

<body>
<Header />

<main class="menu-page">

  <section class="intro">
    <p class="eyebrow">A Jammin Life</p>

    <h1>Preorder: The Next Pastry Drop</h1>

    <p>
      Each Jammin Pastry Drop features a limited menu made fresh in small batches. The menu changes every week depending on seasonal ingredients, inspiration,
      and what I’m excited to bake. Check back here for the newest weekly menu.

    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="box-info">
    <h2>How Each Pastry Drop Works</h2>

    <p>
      Every preorder is sold <strong>by the box rather than by individual pastries.</strong>
    </p>

    <p>
      Each week's box includes <strong>one of every pastry featured on the menu</strong>,
      allowing you to enjoy the full collection of flavors for that week.
    </p>

    <p>
      Because every pastry is baked in limited quantities, individual substitutions
      are generally unavailable. If you have a food allergy or dietary restriction,
      please reach out before ordering and I’ll do my best to accommodate when possible.
    </p>

    <p>
      My goal is to create a tasting experience rather than simply selling pastries —
      each weekly menu is designed to be enjoyed as a complete collection.
    </p>
  </section>

<div class="gallery-wrapper">
  <div class="pastry-gallery">
    <img src="/images/pastry1.jpeg" alt="croissant">
    <img src="/images/pastry6.jpg" alt="pastries">
    <img src="/images/pastry3.png" alt="pistachio croissant">
    <img src="/images/pastry4.jpeg" alt="financier">
    <img src="/images/pastry5.jpeg" alt="croissants">
  </div>
</div>

  <section class="menu-image-section">
    <img src="/images/weekly-menu.png" alt="This week's menu for A Jammin Life" />
  </section>

  <section class="jammin-difference">
    <h2>The Jammin Difference</h2>

    <p>
      Every pastry is made with my signature multigrain dough. Alongside premium white wheat flour, I incorporate 
      whole wheat, einkorn, rye, and spelt to add layers of nutty, earthy flavor and a little more depth to every bite. 
      The result is a pastry that's still buttery
      and indulgent, but with a little extra complexity and a touch of wholesomeness.
    </p>
  </section>

<section class="pickup-info">
  <h2>Next Drop Details</h2>

  <div class="info-grid">
    <div>
      <h3>Pickup Location</h3>
      <p>
        1405 Point St<br />
        Baltimore, MD 21231
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3>Date &amp; Time</h3>
      <p>
        July 25, 2026<br />
        10:00 AM–12:00 PM
      </p>
    </div>

<div>
  <h3>How to Buy</h3>

  <p class="drop-note">
    Every pastry drop is made in limited quantities. Complete the order form below to reserve your Jammin Box!
  </p>

  <a
    class="order-button"
    href="PASTE-YOUR-ORDER-FORM-LINK-HERE"
    target="_blank"
    rel="noopener noreferrer"
  >
    Place an Order
  </a>
</div>
  </div>
</section>

</main>

</body>
</html>

<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: "Josefin Sans", sans-serif;
  background: #fff;
  color: #111;
}

.menu-page {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 4rem 2rem 6rem;
}

.intro {
  text-align: center;
  max-width: 850px;
  margin: 0 auto 4rem;
}

.eyebrow {
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  font-size: 0.5rem;
  color: #777;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

h1 {
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.2rem);
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.1;
  margin: 0 0 2rem;
}

.intro p {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
}

.box-info,
.jammin-difference {
  max-width: 720px;
  margin: 0 auto 5rem;
  padding: 2.5rem 2.75rem;
  border: 1px solid #cfcfcf;
  text-align: center;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

.box-info h2,
.jammin-difference h2 {
  font-size: 2.2rem;
  font-weight: 400;
  margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
}

.box-info p,
.jammin-difference p {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
}

.box-info p:last-child,
.jammin-difference p:last-child {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}

.menu-image-section {
  max-width: 850px;
  margin: 0 auto 5rem;
}

.menu-image-section img {
  width: 100%;
  display: block;
  border: 1px solid #eee;
}

.pickup-info {
  border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
  padding-top: 4rem;
}

.pickup-info h2 {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 400;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  text-align: center;
}

.drop-note {
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.order-button {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 0.9rem 1.6rem;
  background: #174e63;
  color: white;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  transition: background 0.2s ease;
}

.order-button:hover {
  background: #123d4d;
}

.info-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 3rem;
}

.info-grid div {
  border: 1px solid #ddd;
  padding: 2rem;
}

.info-grid h3 {
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.info-grid p {
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.order-button {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 0.75rem;
  padding: 0.9rem 1.35rem;
  background: #174e63;
  color: #ffffff;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-family: "Josefin Sans", sans-serif;
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1;
  border: 1px solid #174e63;
  transition:
    background 0.2s ease,
    color 0.2s ease,
    transform 0.2s ease;
}

.order-button:hover {
  background: #ffffff;
  color: #174e63;
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}
.gallery-wrapper {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  margin: 2.5rem 0 3rem;
}

.pastry-gallery {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.8rem;

  width: fit-content;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.pastry-gallery img {
  width: 155px !important;
  height: 225px !important;
  min-width: 155px;
  max-width: 155px;

  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: 10px;
  display: block;
  transition: transform .2s ease;
}

.pastry-gallery img:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
}

@media (max-width: 800px) {
  .menu-page {
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem 5rem;
  }

  .intro p,
  .box-info p,
  .jammin-difference p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
  }

  .box-info,
  .jammin-difference {
    max-width: 100%;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .info-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .pastry-gallery {
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    max-width: 380px;
  }
.pastry-gallery img {
  width: 115px !important;
  height: 165px !important;
  min-width: 115px;
  max-width: 115px;
}

}
</style>